    public static class Bing3WebDocumentSourceDescriptor.AttributeBuilder
extends Bing3DocumentSourceDescriptor.AttributeBuilder
    Attribute map builder for the Bing3WebDocumentSource component. You can use this builder as a type-safe alternative to populating the attribute map using attribute keys.
